#Coditor is a PHP based lightweight code editor/compiler that supports multiple languages (mentioned in tested with languages section).
Coditor features dark and light mode themes with the option to change the orientation from portrait to landscape.
Coditor also supports user desired text color and font size. Save/download your code from Coditor with the click of a button.

--Technologies Used--
=> Html
=> CSS
=> Javascript
=> jQuery
=> PHP


-- Installation --
=> Download and Paste the directory contents in your server's root folder.
=> You can rename the project directory as per your requirement.
=> You can now run the project and start Coding with Coditor. 

-- Tested With Languages (Runs) --
=> HTML
=> CSS
=> Javascript
=> jQuery
=> PHP

Screenshots are available in the "Project Screenshots" folder.
